cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use Mambo or MamboBench, please cite this work."
title: "Mambo: Mixed Vocal Utterance Parsing for a DAW Producer Co-Pilot"
abstract: >-
  Jointly segmenting and transcribing utterances that interleave spoken
  instructions with hummed melody (and vocal percussion) into a structured
  representation (mambo.utterance.v1), with a producer-co-pilot application that
  emits a replayable action plan and MIDI. Includes MamboBench, a benchmark for
  Mixed Vocal Utterance Parsing.
version: "0.1.0"
date-released: "2026-06-18"
authors:
  - family-names: Karaca
    given-names: Ufuk
    affiliation: "Rodyr, Inc."
# AI tools (Claude Opus 4.8, Claude Fable 5) implemented and evaluated the system under
